fg_segments: WhenToWork, Inc. Privacy Policy What this Privacy Policy Covers
This Privacy Policy covers WhenToWork.com's treatment of information entered into WhenToWork.com when you use the WhenToWork.com site, and when you use WhenToWork.com's services.

Information Sharing and Disclosure WhenToWork will not sell, rent or disclose your personally identifiable information to anyone unless required to do so by law, legal process, litigation, and/or requests from public and governmental authorities within or outside your country of residence.
Your Ability to Edit / Delete Your Account Information
WhenToWork.com gives you the ability to sign in and edit or delete your WhenToWork.com Account Information and preferences at any time.
You can request that your email be removed from WhenToWork.com by emailing Security
Your WhenToWork.com Account Information is password-protected for your privacy and security.
WhenToWork.com uses industry-standard SSL-encryption to protect data transmissions. Each WhenToWork.com user should use their own ID/password for access to ensure security.
Changes to this Privacy Policy WhenToWork.com may amend this policy from time to time.

If we make any substantial changes in the way we use your personal information, we will notify you by posting an announcement on the home page of subscriber manager accounts WhenToWork, Inc.(WhenToWork.com) takes your privacy seriously.
